        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued September 5 at 9:18PM PDT until September 5 at 10:00PM PDT by NWS Las Vegas NV</headline>
        <description>At 917 PM PDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 21 miles north of
Aliante, moving east at 10 mph.

HAZARD...Golf ball size hail and 60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect hail
damage to roofs, windows, and vehicles. Expect wind damage
to roofs and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Gass Pk and Hayford Pk.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
